WEBVTT

00:06.841 --> 00:10.219
If you're bonkers for Bollywood, you've come to the right place.

00:12.564 --> 00:18.357
Mumbai is the glittering epicenter of India's gargantuan Hindi language film industry.

00:19.085 --> 00:21.935
Every part of India has its regional film industry,...

00:22.313 --> 00:25.037
...but Bollywood continues to entrance the nation...

00:25.369 --> 00:28.847
...with its winning escapist formula of masala entertainment,...

00:29.280 --> 00:31.709
...where all singing, all dancing lovers...

00:32.048 --> 00:34.634
...fight and conquer the forces keeping them apart.

